snippet.title: OFFICIAL: Amber Heard in Aquaman 2 - But Idiot DC Fans Mad Keaton's Replacing Ben Affleck
snippet.description:
Idiotic DC Fans Freak Out At Michael Keaton Replacing Ben Affleck As Batman on a billboard because of Zack Snyder's Restore The Snyderverse campaign... But they aren't mad that Mera is officially back in Aquaman 2. Ugh.
